<topic id='class_service.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Class: SERVICE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
A service provided by an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 which may be chargeable to one or more 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nhs_service_agreement">NHS SERVICE AGREEMENTS</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
In most cases, the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
 will be for the direct benefit of a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
 associated with a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_spell">Care Spell</xref>
 may be treatment carried out by the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 acting as the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Provider</xref>
 as part of a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_spell">Care Spell</xref>
 for which the lead responsibility is with another 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_service_type">SERVICE TYPE</xref>
 provides a list of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
